section.name: Struts-Faces Download

Nightly builds of the Struts-Faces Integration Library are available from
http://cvs.apache.org/builds/struts/nightly/struts-faces/.

section.name: Struts-Faces Issue Tracking
section.p: Please report any bugs, or log any enhancement requests, in the Apache Issue Tracking System, using product Struts and component Struts-Faces Library.
